quran[33]{c,v,t,f}:
  74,49,"Kí ló mú wọn ná tí wọ́n ń gbúnrí kúrò níbi ìrántí"
  74,50,"bí ẹni pé àwọn ni kẹ́tẹ́kẹ́tẹ́ tó ń sá lọ,"
  74,51,"tó sá fún kìnìhún?"
  77,37,"Ègbé ni ní ọjọ́ yẹn fún àwọn olùpe-òdodo-nírọ́."
  77,38,"Èyí ni ọjọ́ ìpínyà. Àwa yó sì kó ẹ̀yin àti àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́ jọ."
  77,39,"Tí ẹ bá ní ète kan lọ́wọ́, ẹ déte sí Mi wò."
  78,34,"àti ife ọtí tó kún dẹnu (ni ẹ̀san wọn)."
  78,35,"Wọn kò níí gbọ́ ìsọkúsọ àti ọ̀rọ̀ irọ́ nínú rẹ̀."
  78,36,"(Ó jẹ́) ẹ̀san láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ, (ó sì jẹ́) ọrẹ ní ìbámu sí ìṣírò-iṣẹ́ (wọn)."
  79,28,"Allāhu gbé àjà rẹ̀ ga sókè. Ó sì ṣe é ní pípé tó gún régé."
  79,29,"Ó ṣe òru rẹ̀ ní dúdú. Ó sì fa ìyálẹ̀ta rẹ̀ yọ jáde."
  79,30,"Àti ilẹ̀, Ó tẹ́ ẹ pẹrẹsẹ lẹ́yìn ìyẹn.{1}.",footnotes:1:Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Baƙọrah; 2:29.
  80,25,"Dájúdájú Àwa ń rọ òjò ní púpọ̀."
  80,26,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A mú ilẹ̀ sán kànkàn."
  80,27,"A sì mú kóró èso hù jáde láti inú rẹ̀;"
  81,22,"Àti pé ẹni yín (Ànábì Muhammad - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -) kì í ṣe wèrè."
  81,23,"Ó kúkú rí i nínú òfurufú kedere.{1}.",footnotes:1:Ìyẹn ni pé, Ànábì Muhammad - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - fojú ara rẹ̀ rí Mọlāika Jibrīl - kí ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - nínú òfurufú kedere.
  81,24,"Àti pé kì í ṣe ahun (tàbí ẹni-afurasí) lórí ìró ìkọ̀kọ̀ (tí A fi ránṣẹ́ sí i)."
  82,16,"Wọn kò sì níí kúrò nínú rẹ̀."
  82,17,"Kí sì ni ó mú ọ mọ ohun tó ń jẹ́ Ọjọ́ ẹ̀san?"
  82,18,"Lẹ́yìn náà, kí ni ó mú ọ mọ ohun tó ń jẹ́ Ọjọ́ ẹ̀san?"
  83,13,"Nígbà tí wọ́n bá ń ké àwọn āyah Wa fún un, ó máa wí pé: “Àwọn àkọsílẹ̀ àlọ́ àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́ (nìwọ̀nyí).”"
  83,14,"Rárá (al-Ƙur’ān kì í ṣe àkọsílẹ̀ àlọ́ àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́) bí kò ṣe pé ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe níṣẹ́ aburú l’ó jọba lórí ọkàn wọn."
  83,15,"Rárá (kò rí bí wọ́n ṣe rò ó sí sẹ́), dájúdájú wọn yóò wà nínú gàgá, wọn kò sì níí rí Olúwa wọn ní ọjọ́ yẹn."
  84,10,"Ní ti ẹni tí wọ́n bá sì fún ní ìwé iṣẹ́ rẹ̀ láti ẹ̀yìn rẹ̀,{1}.",footnotes:1:Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Hāƙƙọh; 69:25.
  84,11,"láìpẹ́ ó máa kígbe ìparun."
  84,12,"Ó sì máa wọ inú Iná tó ń jó."
  85,7,"Wọ́n sì ń wo ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe fún àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo."
  85,8,"Wọn kò rí àlèébù kan (wọn kò sì kórira kiní kan) lára wọn bí kò ṣe pé, wọ́n ní ìgbàgbọ́ òdodo nínú Allāhu, Alágbára, Ẹlẹ́yìn,"
  85,9,"Ẹni tí Ó ni ìjọba àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀. Allāhu sì ni Ẹlẹ́rìí lórí gbogbo n̄ǹkan."
  86,1,"(Allāhu) fi sánmọ̀ àti Tọ̄riƙ búra."
  86,2,"Kí sì ni ó mú ọ mọ ohun tó ń jẹ́ Tọ̄riƙ?"
  86,3,"Ìràwọ̀ tí ìmọ́lẹ̀ rẹ̀ ń tàn ròrò (ní alẹ́ ni)."